**Implemented** (commit `1e94690`, 6 files, +356/-2):

**Backend** (`internal/api/server.go`, `internal/api/dto.go`):
- `PATCH /api/features/{id}` — partial update of title and/or priority only. Reloads feature first (preserves immutable fields id/intake_path/spec_dir/current_phase/created_at), validates (`empty_title`/`title_too_long`/`invalid_priority`), rejects `in_progress`/`waiting_for_feedback`/`gate_blocked` with 409 `feature_processing`, sets `updated_at`. Pointer-type DTO so omitted fields aren't zeroed.
- `DELETE /api/features/{id}` — hard delete via existing `ON DELETE CASCADE` schema. 409 `feature_processing` when mid-run (`IsProcessing` + `IsSessionAlive`), 400 `not_deletable` for non-deletable statuses, 204 on success, 404 `feature_not_found` for unknown id.

**UI** (`ui/src/api/client.ts`, `ui/src/types/index.ts`, `ui/src/pages/FeatureDetail.tsx`, `ui/src/components/FeatureCard.tsx`):
